scene/extends-not-found

  × extends target `ghost` not found on the scene search path
  help: Scene-search-path rungs (in order): `./.ark/scenes/<name>.kdl`, `${XDG_CONFIG_HOME}/<appname>/scenes/<name>.kdl`, built-in shipped scenes. Either create the parent scene file or adjust the
        `extends` argument.
